name: r-gstat
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.0-9" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-gstat
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/gstat_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/gstat/gstat_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 122c032c2e15388496853597ebcb5664e76cda96b164e9917ee66d1c24fba4a6

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/


requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-fnn
    - r-lattice
    - r-sp >=0.9_72
    - r-spacetime >=1.0_0
    - r-zoo
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-fnn
    - r-lattice
    - r-sp >=0.9_72
    - r-spacetime >=1.0_0
    - r-zoo

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('gstat')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('gstat')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/r-spatial/gstat/
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Variogram modelling; simple, ordinary and universal point or block (co)kriging; spatio-temporal kriging; sequential Gaussian or indicator (co)simulation; variogram and variogram map plotting utility functions; supports sf and stars.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - jsignell

# Package: gstat
# Version: 2.0-3
# Title: Spatial and Spatio-Temporal Geostatistical Modelling, Prediction and Simulation
